    • Method Detail

      • processIncomingVehicle

        public void processIncomingVehicle(java.util.Date inTime)
        processIncomingVehicle is built to simulate incoming of vehicle in parking. In a try/catch/finally instruction, it will :
        • call getNextParkingNumberIfAvailable method
        • update ParkingSpot
        • set and save new ticket
        Parameters:
        inTime - inTime of incoming vehicle
        Since:
        3.0

      • getNextParkingNumberIfAvailable

        public ParkingSpot getNextParkingNumberIfAvailable()
        getNextParkingNumberIfAvailable is built to get next parking number if available using parkingSpotDAO.getNextAvailableSlot(parkingType).
        Returns:
        parkingSpot Parking spot

      • processExitingVehicle

        public void processExitingVehicle()
        processExitingVehicle is built to simulate outgoing of vehicle in parking. In a try/catch/finally instruction, it will :
        • call getTicket from ticketDAO
        • set out time
        • call calculateFare from fareCalculatorService
        • call updateParking from ticketDAO
        Since:
        3.0
